{"tid":611302,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無熟巴黎既巴絲打？","createTime":"2018-03-30T23:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T16:40:21.000Z","uid":176181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e71e6c84950f323db8b7b62775fcfbfdb09504","tid":611302,"uid":176181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T23:41:29.000Z","msg":"小弟乜都無睇就plan左住係第18區 （jules joffrin)站附近<br />\n<br />\n想問第18區係咪真係咁危險？<br />\n<br />\n題外話 朝早（早上6點左右搭metro會唔會好危險）？"},{"pid":"d14adcd448ff35eabc8b74103e646c89a692c82c","tid":611302,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"坐metro咩時間坐都要保持警覺，唔好企近車門"},{"pid":"2299ec2005eb71c45ab6e9c2539f379c130163de","tid":611302,"uid":176181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14adcd448ff35eabc8b74103e646c89a692c82c","tid":611302,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"坐metro咩時間坐都要保持警覺，唔好企近車門"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁18區真係個到講咁危險？"},{"pid":"839ae5c3a223f36fdc5316f955e9d5cafae30712","tid":611302,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2299ec2005eb71c45ab6e9c2539f379c130163de","tid":611302,"uid":176181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14adcd448ff35eabc8b74103e646c89a692c82c","tid":611302,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"坐metro咩時間坐都要保持警覺，唔好企近車門"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:54:32.000Z","msg":"咁18區真係個到講咁危險？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"18區淨係去過聖心堂個頭，好多騙徒揾食，仲試過被幾個黑人係大街度包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傳統上個區都係紅燈區黎，自己一個去就要更加小心"},{"pid":"da02e9be97141e9b4e531ee7967d5e0ad1f20f3a","tid":611302,"uid":169141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"之前住過18同19區中間範圍既hostel 覺得冇咩<br />\n可能因為我通常都天黑曬之前番到（自己一個）<br />\n<br />\n不過真係好多中國人 係巴黎長住個d係到擺檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fa3ae7edade4ca840ab9ddc29fbd4c28339a71","tid":611302,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"上次去巴黎真係好拿緊張, 周圍都有D 手繩黨, 簽名黨, 仲有D賣鐵塔手信嘅小販<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過so far 無事, 問路亦遇到好人(有問過黑人/女人), 真係好睇你彩數<br />\n<br />\n反而之後行程去到葡萄牙porto, 西班牙馬德里, 巴塞, 感覺太平D, 輕鬆好多"},{"pid":"5fadee408fd5f14b0d456072255ea905baab5839","tid":611302,"uid":27003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"我就住係嗰邊附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實唔覺有咩危險 只係附近多D 黑人<br />\n試過凌晨3,4 點出去撘巴士 條街無乜人"},{"pid":"658ca93c747dcf0ab423b571d54c1f07a3afc450","tid":611302,"uid":95402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"聽講4-6月法國大罷工，嚟緊5月尾會去巴黎旅行，有冇巴絲知嗰邊依家咩情況，交通會唔會真係停哂？"},{"pid":"339a9400fd948676425cbbad13f56a3f6d42c93e","tid":611302,"uid":176181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fadee408fd5f14b0d456072255ea905baab5839","tid":611302,"uid":27003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"我就住係嗰邊附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實唔覺有咩危險 只係附近多D 黑人<br />\n試過凌晨3,4 點出去撘巴士 條街無乜人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意留tg問少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a240c583a068a3a6d9cf0154aebf96177ad02da","tid":611302,"uid":27003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339a9400fd948676425cbbad13f56a3f6d42c93e","tid":611302,"uid":176181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fadee408fd5f14b0d456072255ea905baab5839","tid":611302,"uid":27003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"我就住係嗰邊附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實唔覺有咩危險 只係附近多D 黑人<br />